title: Ziwe and Sutton are suffering too!
description:
Happy RHOBH premiere weeks!!!! Casey and Danielle are back and joined once again by the iconique Ziwe, who gets vulnerable and shares her own misfortune of losing a coat at customs. So. Much like Sutton- we all have problems!

To watch BITCH SESH LIVE on VOD until Tuesday go to Loopedlive.com or the gals'  Instagrams:
@CaseyRoseWilson
@DanielleCarolineSchneider
(And see Danielle in ass less chaps and Casey pee in a cup.)

Season 2 of ZIWE is streaming now on Showtime!
